net.proteusframework.users.audit

Interface Auditable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    FullyAuditable, PrincipalAuditable, TimeAuditable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAuditableEntity, AbstractAuditableSoftDeleteEntity, FullyAuditableImpl, Principal, Role

    public interface Auditable
    This is a tag interface used to make the check for different types of auditable entities less expensive for non-auditable entities. No object should need to directly implement this interface. Important: Any entity implementing this interface must have a Long (or long) for the hibernate ID.
    Author:
    Ken Logan (ken@i2rd.com)
